name: GNU Octave
description: GNU Octave is an advanced programming language compatible with Matlab. Mainly used for numberic calculation. It provides a convenient command line way, and can solve numberic linear and non-linear problems, and perform some numberic simulations.

zh_CN.description: GNU Octave是一种高级编程语言，这种语言与Matlab兼容，主要用于数值计算。它提供了一个方便的命令行方式，可以数值求解线性和非线性问题，以及做一些数值模拟。
